  <summary date="2020-04-30T15:53:21Z" status="Introduced in House">Restore America's Main Street Act

This bill provides a small business with $1.5 million or less in gross receipts and not more than 50 full-time employees a refundable tax credit (rebate) equal to the lesser of 30% of its gross receipts for the first taxable year beginning in 2019, or $120,000. The credit is also available to certain charitable organizations.</summary>
